## **How to Run the Project Locally**

### **1. Clone the repository**

```bash
git clone https://github.com/sairangasaketh/Employee-Attendance-System.git
cd Employee-Attendance-System
```

### **2. Install dependencies**

```bash
npm install
# or
bun install
```

### **3. Create an environment file**

```
VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID="azwexqkwydrtqbzxbwsu"
VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY="eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJzdXBhYmFzZSIsInJlZiI6ImF6d2V4cWt3eWRydHFienhid3N1Iiwicm9sZSI6ImFub24iLCJpYXQiOjE3NjQ0MDM4NzksImV4cCI6MjA3OTk3OTg3OX0.BCSJAFILhNKE5xXJ3dyPRW7TA6CgNai37kGuC7hFzDQ"
VITE_SUPABASE_URL="https://azwexqkwydrtqbzxbwsu.supabase.co"

```

### **4. Start the development server**

```bash
npm run dev
```

Runs at: [http://localhost:5173](http://localhost:5173)

